{"tid":96553,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我的麻糬記趣 (唐狗)","createTime":"2017-01-27T02:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T06:36:38.000Z","uid":75256,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b944cf528b1de222b2dcb9f4c10699fb880f8628","tid":96553,"uid":75256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:40:45.000Z","msg":"小弟初到貴境，開post 貼下我個(乖囡)麻糬相俾大家 <del>J</del> 分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pscz9v36\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpscz9v36&h=9c8535d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻就係黑唐麻糬(簡稱：麻糬)啦！唐狗女，10個月大。我地兩口子本來養緊一隻比熊同一隻貴婦，之後我地想養多一隻，我太太提議不如今次收養啦，而我自己一直都希望養比較大隻ge 狗，於是上網搵領養群組啦。<br />\n<br />\n麻糬係上年4月俾義工係停車場發現，聽講當時有4兄弟姊妹(而家已經有晒住家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，照顧左差唔多一個月就開放領養。第一眼見到佢，毛茸茸，成粒波咁，所以改左個名叫黑唐麻糬。<br />\n<br />\n細個ge 麻糬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qbm35dso\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqbm35dso&h=0c3fd316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前仲係好細隻，只係大過手掌少少 (而家可以撞死人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a12se068\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa12se068&h=069f25a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浪浪肚裡面應該好多寄生蟲，但餵左兩次康圖都唔覺佢有痾蟲，寵物鋪老闆就介紹一隻杜蟲藥，食左一次...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/14568_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fcontent%2Fphoto%2Fv1%2F14568_WM.jpg&h=0f3defa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成堆蟲痾出來，之前仲以為佢比較乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面張相係食完第二次映，蟲少左但都幾噁心，唔貼圖啦，貼拎自己睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/w19cqznu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw19cqznu&d=cFyyBEaL9oyRSxvD5eL3%2B2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=d931a58c\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/w19cqznu</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時講住咁多先，有機會再分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請支持領養 不棄養<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9kyno7xp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9kyno7xp&h=d1bb4f64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8313e66749b6607901bb1e4b374738bd0d99d97","tid":96553,"uid":37530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:42:35.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"ada5d2df3e5d9f729f7ce850676c621bf7ab9032","tid":96553,"uid":30568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:53:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61e04830c540ca19fdb6246106a1f74d9f5085dd","tid":96553,"uid":12181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:51:24.000Z","msg":"唐唐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9043c609130188417d5ab658f8463b7e311923e","tid":96553,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c090bd0f61e2dbc4e9caf2b3486febf034f9dd09","tid":96553,"uid":50828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"個樣好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb05036391d2d3b11da549596cacc03bb516b20a","tid":96553,"uid":76120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"麻糬好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257090afa90c702f4ce5e1b28dd4666d2475a7a2","tid":96553,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl