ts/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864441c2b05c8f4cee659405a4352eb23d526bdd","tid":96553,"uid":75256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:37:08.000Z","msg":"年三十晚罐罐晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左起: 二家姐牛牛 (貴婦), 大家姐熊熊(比熊) &amp; 細妹麻糬(唐狗)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xm1ky3uj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxm1ky3uj&h=be62cedf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"011b9cec5c6c4195f182f31658495d3817d28347","tid":96553,"uid":13653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"好型呀住黑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a74a820e8a6e68f48d3498d01fe2be8359bfdae","tid":96553,"uid":13653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好型呀全黑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cdc3dfce3d9256323d6c798456fc6fcf822d4cf5","tid":96553,"uid":56909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得罪講句 樓主咁養咁多隻狗 最qq係呢隻黑色唐狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ad393e06ec24151ea59f4a195002748f83d49b","tid":96553,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:34:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年三十晚罐罐晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左起: 二家姐牛牛 (貴婦), 大家姐熊熊(比熊) &amp;amp; 細妹麻糬(唐狗)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xm1ky3uj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxm1ky3uj&h=be62cedf&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係細妹最得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfdacb9dfe55dc5bd1e5fe8b6089ff5f53af740","tid":96553,"uid":75256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:45:38.000Z","msg":"見到好多巴絲打話麻糬得意, 其實佢都有崩壞一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (熊熊按: Daddy 快啲貼阿妹醜樣相等大家笑下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ocgf527b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Focgf527b&h=125bed67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張係佢初時ge 相, 日日流住行鼻涕, 個樣又薯下薯下咁, 真係無改錯名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l2y9vadt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl2y9vadt&h=c053b67c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到大個少少啦, 就成日發呆, 係度思考狗生。 到而家有時都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uwjrdapt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuwjrdapt&h=e9e09c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當佢做錯事閙佢時, 佢反應又激死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我聽唔到~咩都聽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vso4zftn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvso4zftn&h=3c4c1232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDaddy 講完未呀～ 好眼瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/su58nczy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsu58nczy&h=4174e8b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7ec6f2f4ae3cd1aecd6dea718439cf88488c32e","tid":96553,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:01:39.000Z","msg":"流住行鼻涕都好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好傻<br />\n唐狗黎講真係算好靚"},{"pid":"12798471a9af9de8c737fe0a626a1202716d0ec0","tid":96553,"uid":67036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:06:37.000Z","msg":"麻糬住邊區呀？好想換下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a627bf1e8d07c29d0edba5d8a6958fd587e3ff","tid":96553,"uid":67036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麻糬住邊區呀？好想換下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n摸*自膠"},{"pid":"c239147472a464636cc58cfabc46f2f69757f471","tid":96553,"uid":56909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"啲圖次次都要側頭睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb714afee4f3d0470b32ad97f07c1536f9e95250","tid":96553,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T12:13:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年三十晚罐罐晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左起: 二家姐牛牛 (貴婦), 大家姐熊熊(比熊) &amp;amp; 細妹麻糬(唐狗)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xm1ky3uj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxm1ky3uj&h=be62cedf&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n身形差咁遠玩唔玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f745974e0571c930c04f3bd4eb508859d2c2c66","tid":96553,"uid":64514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唐狗！ 好靚"},{"pid":"ff6ef63332bb57e27f0c7cc36528b221cd658e64","tid":96553,"uid":75256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲圖次次都要側頭睇<img src=\"/assets/